test_even_range:
assert [44, 46, 48] == [48]
  At index 0 diff: 44 != 48
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 46
  Full diff:
  - [48]
  + [44, 46, 48]
test_large_range:
assert [22, 23, 24] == [24]
  At index 0 diff: 22 != 24
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 23
  Full diff:
  - [24]
  + [22, 23, 24]
